flowRoot.flowPara: Due to the threat of contagious disease (COVID-19) please accept alternates to handshakes, such as Vulcan Salute, in place of traditional handshakes until vaccines are at warp drive. This Star Trek greeting means "Live long and Prosper," and is used to wish friends, family, business partners, and others prosperity and health.
